## Daily Run (8am {{ owner.timezone | default('ET') }} cron — skip at other intervals)

### Step 1 — Research Pipeline

```bash
cd {{ server.analytics_path | default('/opt/cmo-analytics') }} && source venv/bin/activate
python scripts/research_pipeline.py --no-summary 2>/dev/null || echo "Research pipeline not configured"
```

Output saved to: `{{ server.analytics_path | default('/opt/cmo-analytics') }}/research/learnings/research-scan-YYYY-MM-DD.md`

Distill top 3–5 findings, post to #research.

### Step 2 — Industry Signal Scan (daily)

Check relevant subreddits, HN, and industry feeds for emerging tools and patterns.
Flag anything relevant to {% for product in products %}{{ product.name }}{% if not loop.last %}, {% endif %}{% endfor %}.

### Step 3 — Harness 30-Day Performance Check (date-triggered)

```bash
python3 -c "
import json
from datetime import datetime
from pathlib import Path
checks = list(Path('{{ server.analytics_path | default('/opt/cmo-analytics') }}/data/pending_checks').glob('*.json'))
today = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')
due = [c for c in checks if json.loads(c.read_text()).get('check_after','') <= today and json.loads(c.read_text()).get('status') == 'pending']
print(len(due))
"
```

If output > 0: run the full performance loop:
```bash
cd {{ server.analytics_path | default('/opt/cmo-analytics') }} && source venv/bin/activate
python3 scripts/performance_check.py
python3 scripts/pattern_extract.py
python3 scripts/harness_defaults_update.py
```

Post results to Discord.

